Package: first-steps
Version: 1.0.0-1
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-4.0, gir1.2-adw-1, flatpak, policykit-1
Recommends: ubuntu-drivers-common, timeshift, ufw
Suggests: gnome-tweaks, bottles
Installed-Size: 120
Maintainer: First Steps Contributors <noreply@github.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/Naftaliro/first-steps
Description: GTK4 + LibAdwaita onboarding wizard for Zorin OS 18
 First Steps is a system setup wizard that helps you configure a fresh
 Linux installation through a clean, checkbox-driven interface.
 .
 Features include one-click codec installation, Flatpak/Flathub setup
 with a curated app picker, hardware driver detection, Windows app
 compatibility via Bottles, automatic backup configuration with
 Timeshift, power profile management, UFW firewall setup, accessibility
 settings, and GNOME theme switcher integration.
 .
 Designed for Zorin OS 18 and other Ubuntu 24.04-based distributions.
